@node run " Log User v1.1 by Glen Martin of GREMLiNS BBS"
@{"°°" link grems}
  _____         _        _ _
 |_   _|_ _  __| |_ __ _| | |
  |   || ' \(_-<  _/ _` | | |
 |_____|_||_/__/\__\__,_|_|_|                        @{b}(c) GREMLiNS MAXsWARE@{ub}

 Firstly (if you already haven't) create a new directory called "gremlins"
 in your doors directory. Assign "gremlins" to your doors path in the user
 startup sequence, eg: "assign gremlins: doors:gremlins" assuming you also
 have the doors path assigned, you spastic.

 Move the "Log_User" directory  into the "gremlins" dir & run door via the
 Introdoor.text sequence (..and SysOp menu, if you desire).

 Have probs or want to send a msg then @{"contact" link call} me.

@endnode
