 Use this door at your own risk, it's provided as is... So don't blame me!

 -------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Due to a number of reasons,  GREMLiNS BBS is now a  Private and Mail Only
 System.  It was a big (..and sad)  decision to do this,  but no matter, I
 am still around,  supporting MAX's and Fluffy (..and the Amiga).  I would
 like to say thanks to all my  users and  members who called and supported
 this great BBS.  The past few years  has been fun,  but things change and
 life goes on... Thanks again and keep in touch, I will!  Email me, Cya..!

 -------------------------------------------------------------------------

 My overseas plans are still alive,  and am looking forward  to travelling
 and meeting all you Fluffy pple. Hopefully more sooner than later?! Still
 am studying and setting goals and all that, so life is A O K... for now!?

 Enjoy... ... . .. .

@endnode
